com.ualberta.cmput301w17t22.moodswing

Class EmotionalState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ualberta.cmput301w17t22.moodswing.EmotionalState

  • public class EmotionalState
extends java.lang.Object
    An EmotionalState is the user entered emotional state of a MoodEvent.

    Contains the information associated with a pre-defined emotional state. This includes its description which is the name of the emotion and the drawable id for the attached emoticon.

    Version:
    2017-02-18
    Author:
    Fred
    See Also:
    Participant, MoodEvent
